RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 1 300 Y Dirt CR: 65. Speed Index Race Purse 7500. For Three Year Olds and Upward With An Average Speed Index Of 65 And Under or With A Speed Index That Has Never Been Better Than 70.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ALL OUTTA SUGAR never in doubt. HANOVER HILL JUSTINE very game second. BEWITCHIN no match, top two. BAR EF RUSHFURRCANDY broke outward, no closing kick. CARAWAYS NATIVE LANE broke inward at start.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 2 250 Y Dirt CR: 80. Speed Index Race Purse 9500. For Three Year Olds and Upward With An Average Speed Index Of 85 And Under.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: IM SPEEDY drew away. ZOXTOBEYOU closed well outside. AH WANNA CORONA good effort in between. BODHI hopped at start. MS MEXICAN MOUSE squeezed early, no finish. MIA HAVANA outrun.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 3 250 Y Dirt CR: 67. Speed Index Race Purse 8500. For Three Year Olds and Upward With An Average Speed Index Of 75 And Under.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: UPANDOVER wire to wire. FIRST GOLDEN ROSE DQ to 4th, came in at start. CHICKSGOTMEWONDERIN raced evenly. DM PAID IN ADVANCE rough beginning. KEFLA bumped hard at start.

ENTRY.NAME: Dm Paid in Advance
ENTRY.OWNER: Foster Earl A and Baker Les

ENTRY.NAME: dq-First Golden Rose
ENTRY.COMMENT: DQ to 4th, came in at start

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 4 400 Y Dirt CR: 83. Allowance Purse 12000. For Three Year Olds and Upward Which Have Never Won Five Races or Ontario Breds Which Have Never Won Six Races.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SNOW MOOSE wire to wire. ONE FABULOUS WAVE closed with a rush. HAD TO BE RELENTLESS hopped slightly at start. HANOVER HILL THERESA no closing kick. MOMSEXTRAVAGANTHEART not with these.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 5 110 Y Dirt CR: 72. Allowance Purse 10000. For Three Year Olds and Upward Which have Finished 3rd or Lower in their Last Three Starts at Ajax Downs (last Three Starts must have been at Ajax Downs).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MISS ORIENT EXPRESS drew away late. RUNAWAYLIGHTSNCAVIAR good effort. FAST STREAKIN NICK needed more ground. RAPTER broke a step slow. A FANCY ARRANGEMENT clean trip, no excuse.

ENTRY.NAME: Miss Orient Express
ENTRY.OWNER: Broadstock Marie and Marchand Jean Claude

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 6 300 Y Dirt CR: 73. Speed Index Race Purse 10000. For Three Year Olds and Upward With A Speed Index That Has Never Been Better Than 90.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: KRASH ON OKEY wire to wire. QUEEN CHARLOTTE closed well outside. EYESA COCO PUFF clean trip. JOE CHECKERS broke sluggish. RUBY SUNDAY no closing kick.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: Princess Derby AJAX DOWNS RACE 7 350 Y Dirt CR: 78. Derby Purse 51930. FOR THREE YEAR OLD FILLIES, WHICH MADE THEIR NOMINATION PAYMENTS TO REMAIN ELIGIBLE (TIME TRIALS UNNECESSARY). For further Stakes Race details and Payout Percentages, see QROOI Stakes Book.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FIRSTPRIZE CHARLOTTE DQ to last 10th. HAD TO BE IVY much the best. SILVER LYNING closed with a rush. KATI ON FIRE needed more room. VALIANT CHICK INSNOW roughed up at start. FRANCESCA bumped hard at start. AQUATICA came out at start. DAM IM RELENTLESS no finishing kick. JUST A KVN not a factor. A RUSHN LILLY outrun.
